{"id":118854,"type":6,"name":"さよなら、小津先生","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/e3/66/118854_FNOx4.jpg","summary":"職、名声、家族、財産を失った元エリート銀行マン・小津が再就職までの仕事として私立高校の臨時教師となる。こうして先生となった小津と若者たちの交流を描く学園ドラマ。また大人が子供に教えられ、成長していく姿を描いた作品。\r\n当初はコメディー色が強くなる予定だったが、脚本の君塚良一が第2話を執筆中に9・11事件が発生。衝撃を受けた君塚は、「再生」をテーマに盛り込んだ、よりシリアスな内容に変更した。\r\nなお、3年後の2004年11月26日には、金曜エンタテイメント枠で女子バスケ部を舞台にした続編が放映された。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>再见，小津老师</li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/28119\">田村正和</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>11</li><li><span>开始: </span>2001年10月9日</li><li><span>结束: </span>2001年12月18日</li><li><span>频道: </span>フジテレビ</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0305101</li>","eps":[{"id":450992,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/450992","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":450993,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/450993","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":450994,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/450994","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":450995,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/450995","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":450996,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/450996","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":450997,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/450997","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":450998,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/450998","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":450999,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/450999","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":451000,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/451000","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","stat